    time order. Set the default with `git config undoredo.scope` (edit|global), the log
    density with `undoredo.log` (full|compact), whether `git take` stages with
    `undoredo.take` (unstaged|staged), and color with `undoredo.color` (auto|always|never).
EOF
}

